    "text": "If you are a resident of Virginia, Colorado, Connecticut, Utah, Texas, Oregon, Montana, Iowa, Tennessee, Indiana, Delaware, New Jersey, or any other US state with a comprehensive consumer privacy law, you have rights similar to those described in Section 8. We honor these rights as required by applicable law. Contact privacy@brainwiseenterprises.com to exercise your rights."
